    <abstract>This document examines the use of Source-Specific Multicast (SSM) across inter-domain peering points for a specified set of deployment scenarios.  The objectives are to (1) describe the setup process for multicast-based delivery across administrative domains for these scenarios and (2) document supporting functionality to enable this process.</abstract>
